-- Schlecker Insolvency Admin May Sell ‘Ihr Platz’ Unit, FTD Says
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2012-04-09T15:51:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-09/schlecker-insolvency-admin-may-sell-ihr-platz-unit-ftd-says.html
Schlecker’s insolvency
administrators are seeking to sell the German retailer’s “Ihr
Platz” drugstore chain in case finding a buyer for the entire
company proves too difficult,  Financial Times Deutschland 
reporterd, citing unidentified people in the finance industry.  Consultant firm  Roland Berger  has been tasked with
developing a plan to sell the unit separately, and some
potential buyers have already been approached, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
 crahn2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
